WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Hello and good afternoon.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:08.000
My name is Yesit Pérez. I am the pastor
of Zion Church in Basel.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:11.500
I am Venezuelan
and I come from Caracas.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:16.500
As many people know, my country Venezuela
is currently experiencing a tragedy.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:21.500
I prayed to God a great deal
and asked Him how I could help.

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:26.500
How could I help from here,
from Basel in Switzerland?

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:31.000
Even from here, I can be of great help
to my people in Venezuela.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
That is how the idea arose
to create an aid fund.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.500
We are currently supporting
and assisting two churches:

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:43.500
Bethel Church
and Hermon Church.

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:48.500
We are bringing food and meals
to many people in need.

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:53.500
We invite you
to become part of this aid effort.

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:56.500
We will provide you
with our bank details.

00:00:56.500 --> 00:01:00.000
May God bless you.
Thank you for your support.
